            "answer_text": "You can find how many searches are there for particular keyword by using various types of Keyword Research tools.You can even find an alternative keywords which suits your topic with these tools. 1.Google Keyword Planner is the free tool which provides you the total number of searches for that particular keyword.If you are a newbie blogger you can go with this free tool.For using this you should have Google Adwords account.If you don't have Google Adwords account you can create one for free and start using Keyword tool. If you wish to spend some money for keyword research then you can go with these Pro tools  1.SEMrush 2.Long Tail Pro ",
